'''Nickel''' was an element found in [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroids]], including [[Oris]] and most likely [[Nickel One]]. It was also present on [[Antar 4/Legends|Antar 4]], and [[Ruusan/Legends|Ruusan]] was said to have significant deposits of nickel.<ref name="DF:JK">''[[Dark Forces: Jedi Knight]]''</ref>

